no.steria.osgi.jsr330activator.implementation

Class ProviderAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • no.steria.osgi.jsr330activator.implementation.ProviderAdapter

  • public class ProviderAdapter
extends Object
    This class defines the operations done by the Jsr330Activator on the Provider implementations found inside the bundle. The operations are starting and stopping the provider. Starting the provider means instantiating the provider and causing all injections to be satisfied.
    Author:
    Steinar Bang
